        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="bento-section">
        <div class="bento-body">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white">Security</h3>
          <p class="mt-4 text-gray-300">Deploy with confidence knowing your data is protected with enterprise-grade security.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="bento-section">
        <div class="bento-body">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white">Reliability</h3>
